 was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Maureward was born about 1340, in Coleorton, Leicestershire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with Elizabeth Odingsell. He died on 12 April 1378, in Coleorton, Leicestershire, England, at the age of 39."},"et":{"abt 1340–12 April 1378":"umbes 1340–12. aprill 1378","1340–Female":"1340–Surnud","1360–1424":"1360–1424","1340–1378":"1340–1378","12 April 1378":"12. aprill 1378","1424":"1424","1378":"1378","1340":"1340","abt 1340":"umbes 1340","1360":"1360","Coleorton, Leicestershire, England":"Coleorton, Leicestershire, England","Cole Orton, Leicestershire, England":"Coleorton, Leicestershire, England"},"fi":{"abt 1340–12 April 1378":"noin 1340–12. huhtikuuta 1378","1340–Female":"1340–Kuollut","1360–1424":"1360–1424","1340–1378":"1340–1378","12 April 1378":"12. huhtikuuta 1378","1424":"1424","1378":"1378","1340":"1340","abt 1340":"noin 1340","1360":"1360","Coleorton, Leicestershire, England":"Coleorton, Leicestershire, England","Cole Orton, Leicestershire, England":"Coleorton, Leicestershire, England"},"fr":{"abt 1340–12 April 1378":"environ 1340–12 avril 1378","1340–Female":"1340–Décédée","1360–1424":"1360–1424","1340–1378":"1340–1378","12 April 1378":"12 avril 1378","1424":"1424","1378":"1378","1340":"1340","abt 1340":"environ 1340","1360":"1360","Coleorton, Leicestershire, England":"Coleorton, Leicestershire, Angleterre","Cole Orton, Leicestershire, England":"Coleorton, Leicestershire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"William Maureward est né environ 1340, à Coleorton, Leicestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Elizabeth Odingsell. Il est décédé le 12 avril 1378, à Coleorton, Leicestershire, Angleterre, à l’âge de 39 ans."},"de":{"abt 1340–12 April 1378":"um 1340–12. April 1378","1340–Female":"1340–Verstorben","1360–1424":"1360–1424","1340–1378":"1340–1378","12 A